{
  "lesson": "WC-PB-10",
  "audioMaster": "training/playbooks/WC-PB-10-full-narration-v1.0.mp3",
  "audioDurationS": 214.518,
  "method": "silencedetect -32dB/0.28s within known block windows; proportional fallback",
  "phrases": [
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p01",
      "text": "Start in Settings, under Customer Portal.",
      "startS": 0,
      "endS": 2.394,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p02",
      "text": "The hub names the portal and, right beside it, one chip does the heavy lifting: Live.",
      "startS": 3.031,
      "endS": 7.507,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p03",
      "text": "If that chip isn't showing, nobody signs in and the ticket is portal-wide.",
      "startS": 7.891,
      "endS": 8.405,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p04",
      "text": "It is, so keep going.",
      "startS": 8.991,
      "endS": 13.58,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p05",
      "text": "And leave Publish Changes alone.",
      "startS": 14.145,
      "endS": 17.68,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p06",
      "text": "Now the five tiles across the top.",
      "startS": 18.08,
      "endS": 20.076,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p07",
      "text": "Eighteen hundred forty registered members.",
      "startS": 20.648,
      "endS": 22.965,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p08",
      "text": "Two hundred forty-seven logins today.",
      "startS": 23.316,
      "endS": 25.46,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p09",
      "text": "That second number is your triage: members are getting in right now,",
      "startS": 26.193,
      "endS": 28.14,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p10",
      "text": "so this ticket is probably one account.",
      "startS": 28.384,
      "endS": 32.426,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p11",
      "text": "Zero logins on a live portal means the opposite.",
      "startS": 32.951,
      "endS": 35.842,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p12",
      "text": "Next, the address.",
      "startS": 36.32,
      "endS": 37.701,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p13",
      "text": "Click Copy and compare it to the link the member is using.",
      "startS": 38.082,
      "endS": 40.98,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p14",
      "text": "A stale URL is the most common can't-log-in there is.",
      "startS": 41.35,
      "endS": 45.152,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p15",
      "text": "Then open Preview Portal and try to reproduce what they see.",
      "startS": 45.527,
      "endS": 48.773,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p16",
      "text": "Portal Health backs you up: API connected, certificate valid.",
      "startS": 49.159,
      "endS": 50.463,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p17",
      "text": "The backend is fine.",
      "startS": 50.877,
      "endS": 54.605,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p18",
      "text": "Back on the hub, two cards settle most of these tickets.",
      "startS": 55.093,
      "endS": 58.004,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p19",
      "text": "Access and Security holds the login rules: phone and email, OTP on, thirty-minute sessions.",
      "startS": 58.322,
      "endS": 60.693,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p20",
      "text": "Features and Modules reads seven of nine enabled.",
      "startS": 60.982,
      "endS": 64.135,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p21",
      "text": "For a missing feature, that line is usually the whole answer.",
      "startS": 64.472,
      "endS": 67.134,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p22",
      "text": "Two modules are just off.",
      "startS": 67.512,
      "endS": 72.42,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p23",
      "text": "Open Access and Security and read the login methods.",
      "startS": 73.04,
      "endS": 74.783,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p24",
      "text": "Phone, yes. Email, yes. Membership number, no. Guest access, no.",
      "startS": 75.183,
      "endS": 76.709,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p25",
      "text": "So the member typing their membership number at sign-in isn't broken,",
      "startS": 77.563,
      "endS": 78.745,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p26",
      "text": "and neither is the portal.",
      "startS": 79.381,
      "endS": 80.665,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p27",
      "text": "That method is switched off.",
      "startS": 81.173,
      "endS": 82.129,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p28",
      "text": "Match how they log in against what's actually enabled.",
      "startS": 82.421,
      "endS": 96.034,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p29",
      "text": "Stay on this tab for the quiet culprit: OTP.",
      "startS": 96.544,
      "endS": 98.681,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p30",
      "text": "A one-time code is required on every login, delivered by SMS, and it dies after ten minutes.",
      "startS": 99.051,
      "endS": 99.839,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p31",
      "text": "A wrong or dead mobile number means the code never lands.",
      "startS": 100.579,
      "endS": 106.491,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p32",
      "text": "The password rules sit just below: eight characters minimum, nothing fancier required.",
      "startS": 107.125,
      "endS": 117.28,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p33",
      "text": "Back on the hub, read Recent Portal Activity.",
      "startS": 117.68,
      "endS": 120.638,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p34",
      "text": "One line is worth the whole feed:",
      "startS": 121.206,
      "endS": 123.161,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p35",
      "text": "three failed login attempts on one account, this morning, from mobile.",
      "startS": 123.682,
      "endS": 127.42,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p36",
      "text": "That names the member, counts the tries, stamps the time, and tells you which channel to test.",
      "startS": 127.783,
      "endS": 133.573,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p37",
      "text": "They're reaching the login and getting rejected.",
      "startS": 133.923,
      "endS": 136.228,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p38",
      "text": "For a mobile-app complaint, switch to Digital and open Mobile App Users.",
      "startS": 136.761,
      "endS": 140.994,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p39",
      "text": "Forty-eight hundred twenty users, more than half on iOS.",
      "startS": 142.001,
      "endS": 145.256,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p40",
      "text": "The list below carries the three columns that explain most app tickets:",
      "startS": 145.524,
      "endS": 149.31,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p41",
      "text": "app version, notifications, and status.",
      "startS": 149.534,
      "endS": 152.08,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p42",
      "text": "Find the member's row.",
      "startS": 152.48,
      "endS": 153.786,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p43",
      "text": "Tom Brown is running four point oh five on Android while others are on four point two one.",
      "startS": 155.002,
      "endS": 160.097,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p44",
      "text": "An out-of-date build explains a login that fails or a feature that never appears.",
      "startS": 160.698,
      "endS": 165.345,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p45",
      "text": "Notifications off explains I never get alerts.",
      "startS": 166.061,
      "endS": 169.147,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p46",
      "text": "And status confirms the account itself is active.",
      "startS": 169.517,
      "endS": 172.103,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p47",
      "text": "Now write it up.",
      "startS": 172.56,
      "endS": 173.342,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p48",
      "text": "Portal live, on the right address.",
      "startS": 174.098,
      "endS": 175.904,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p49",
      "text": "Which login method they used against what's enabled.",
      "startS": 176.672,
      "endS": 179.26,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p50",
      "text": "OTP required, delivered by SMS.",
      "startS": 179.615,
      "endS": 182.297,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p51",
      "text": "The failed-login line with its account, count, time, and channel.",
      "startS": 182.751,
      "endS": 186.6,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p52",
      "text": "For mobile, the app version, notifications, and status.",
      "startS": 187.078,
      "endS": 190.462,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p53",
      "text": "Flipping any of those switches happens in production, never here.",
      "startS": 190.797,
      "endS": 194.274,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p54",
      "text": "That's the flow.",
      "startS": 194.72,
      "endS": 195.681,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p55",
      "text": "Read the Live chip and the logins before you blame one account.",
      "startS": 196.269,
      "endS": 199.798,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p56",
      "text": "Check the login methods and OTP when sign-in fails.",
      "startS": 200.854,
      "endS": 204.168,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p57",
      "text": "Read the activity feed for proof.",
      "startS": 205.159,
      "endS": 206.79,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p58",
      "text": "Check the member's app row when it's mobile.",
      "startS": 207.913,
      "endS": 209.927,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p59",
      "text": "Then route it, with nothing published and nothing saved.",
      "startS": 210.485,
      "endS": 214.08,
      "timing": "silence"
    }
  ]
}